data.description: A charming ranch-style house nestled on over an acre of land, boasting meticulously crafted professional landscaping. This picturesque property offers a tranquil escape, with lush greenery and vibrant blooms adorning the expansive grounds. The ranch-style architecture exudes a sense of warmth and comfort, inviting you to relax and enjoy the natural beauty surrounding you. Whether it's lounging on the spacious patio, strolling through manicured gardens, or simply taking in the breathtaking views, this home offers a serene retreat for those who appreciate the finer details of outdoor living.    The interior boasts abundant natural light streaming through large windows, highlighting the beautiful hardwood floors and tasteful finishes throughout. The living room features a cozy fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.  Back inside, the home offers three spacious bedrooms, including a luxurious master suite with a spa-like ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet.
